Sun::Solaris::Kstat for Linux version 0.01
==========================================

This is an implementation of the Sun::Solaris::Kstat Perl module
for Linux ZFS. It should behave identically to the Solaris version.

In this version the hash key has been changed to be compatible with the BSD sysctl 'kstat.zfs.misc.arcstats.xxx' notation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

